# Optional code-to-doc sync rules.
# Format:
# <code path>[,<code path>...]|<doc path>[,<doc path>...]|<message>
# Add repository-specific extensions in .orch/rules/<target>/local.docsync.rules.
#
# Examples:
# internal/config,.env.example|docs/config.md|config changes must update docs
# internal/transport/httpapi,openapi|docs/api.md|api or contract changes must update docs
